    &lt;h1&gt; Goal &lt;/h1&gt;
    In 2023 February, I started a System Analysis and Development Technologist course, and I will use this blog post to make my tests. &lt;br/&gt;
    This website uses Hugo as framework. Hugo uses markdown to create HTML. I am learning HTML and CSS development, and this page is writing directly with this languages &lt;br/&gt;
    Important: This is a Work in Process webpage. As I am in learning process, maybe will be so amateur. If you have some tips, please let me know. &lt;br/&gt;
    I am having some problem yet, as Option List and forms. I will investigate what can be happen.
